article.description: — Jamir Harris posted 19 points and eight assists as American beat Bucknell 78-71 on Saturday.
article.headline: Harris scores 19 to carry American over Bucknell 78-71
article.linkText: Harris scores 19 to carry American over Bucknell 78-71
article.story: LEWISBURG, Pa. -- — Jamir Harris posted 19 points and eight assists as American beat Bucknell 78-71 on Saturday. Stacy Beckton Jr. had 17 points for American (3-5, 3-5 Patriot League). Matt Rogers added 12 points. Ben Lubarsky had 10 points. Deuce Turner had 21 points for the Bison (4-5, 4-5), whose four-game win streak was snapped. Walter Ellis added 13 points. Xander Rice had 10 points and six assists. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
